{"id":"ozias","term":"Ozias","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Son of Joram (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Matthew 1:8\">Matt. 1:8</a>); called also Uzziah (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Kings 15:32\">2 Kings 15:32</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Kings 15:34\">34</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Matthew 1:8","2 Kings 15:32","2 Kings 15:34"]}